    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/7d1a1974076593602ffc2699b8615e99.poster.avif?t=1771107034\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/7d1a1974076593602ffc2699b8615e99.webm?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用各种技能来解谜 🧩。升级、放松、休息，再接再厉 🎮。随着每一次胜利，不断提升你的技能并进化 🌱.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏灵感来自波兰树木通灵师 Weronika Dąbrowska 的著作 📜，并邀请你…「忘记自己，才能记得自己」</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >运用你的力量来解开谜题</h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与森林的灵魂重新连结 🌲，在令人目眩神迷的视觉效果中，仿佛置身于一个抚慰视觉皮层的 ASMR 水疗中心 😌.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/8d45364771432f4ad139e3e9d4a81cab.poster.avif?t=1771107034\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/8d45364771432f4ad139e3e9d4a81cab.webm?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/8d45364771432f4ad139e3e9d4a81cab.mp4?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制定你的策略</h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过发掘以熟悉的生存风格展现出的技能，制定最佳策略 🧠.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/9a66ed5d6c94ac63c26538a8fa611269.poster.avif?t=1771107034\" width=620 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/9a66ed5d6c94ac63c26538a8fa611269.webm?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/9a66ed5d6c94ac63c26538a8fa611269.mp4?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找最佳战利品 🏆</h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏世界充满了神秘的文物：古老的法杖、神秘的宝石 💎、叶子披风 🍃、麋鹿骷髅 🦌💀 以及更多 ✨.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/d5f27476d0ec4c29c6fd1a22392e490f.poster.avif?t=1771107034\" width=620 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/d5f27476d0ec4c29c6fd1a22392e490f.webm?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/d5f27476d0ec4c29c6fd1a22392e490f.mp4?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的树灵</h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让树灵 🌳 在「森林圈」 ✨ 中赋予你它们的力量。管理并策划，确保它们的技能能为你带来最大的效果 💥.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/c86f4e86a070b8578a4940bd2b79e253.poster.avif?t=1771107034\" width=620 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/c86f4e86a070b8578a4940bd2b79e253.webm?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/c86f4e86a070b8578a4940bd2b79e253.mp4?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >清理森林！</h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♻️ 你收集的垃圾越多，森林给予的感激也就越多 💚.</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/74e406039cc3b33fee1e64565be87d5f.poster.avif?t=1771107034\" width=620 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/74e406039cc3b33fee1e64565be87d5f.webm?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192050/extras/74e406039cc3b33fee1e64565be87d5f.mp4?t=1771107034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
